02:33.820 --> 02:39.390
Abbreviated as D F while the columns common Alfas.

02:39.460 --> 02:44.130
Please note that after the 30th row the numbers don't vary that much.

02:44.200 --> 02:50.980
Actually after 30 degrees of freedom the statistic table becomes almost the same as the Z statistic

02:51.730 --> 02:54.310
as the degrees of freedom depend on the sample.

02:54.340 --> 02:59.350
In essence the bigger the sample the closer we get to the actual numbers.

